name: THE SURROGATE
description:
Art and Music by Mike Neff. 7.18.2021.

A Surrogate Nativity in an unknown location somewhere on the Verge. These entities are the scattered vestiges of a once great power. To most, they are nothing but a distant memory of a race of creators and form-givers. To a few who have ventured closer to the Void, they are a face in the darkness that vanishes as quickly as it appears. . . .
